# Testing and Quality

## Backend unit tests

- `clojure.test` in `test/galaticos/` — suffix `*_test.clj`
- Run: `./bin/galaticos test` or `clojure -M:test`

## ClojureScript unit tests

- `test-cljs/` — run `clojure -M:cljs-test`

## E2E

- Playwright specs in `e2e/` — auth, CRUD, dashboard flows
- Run via npm/playwright scripts in `package.json`

## Coverage (PR blocker)

Cloverage alias `:coverage` in `deps.edn`:

- Fails when **min(% lines, % forms)** below **70**
- Some ns excluded via `:ns-exclude-regex` — see `docs/informacao/dominio/testing-coverage.md`

```bash
./bin/galaticos coverage
```

## When to add tests

- New or changed handler/db behavior → matching `test/galaticos/*_test.clj`
- Bug fixes → regression test when feasible

## PR checklist

From `CONTRIBUTING.md`: compile clean, tests pass, coverage threshold, clj-kondo clean, conventional commit message.
